text: Krishna Reddy or Krishnareddy may refer to: * Bojjala Gopala Krishna Reddy (born 1949), Srikalahasti MLA in 1994, 1999 and 2009 * Krishna Reddy (artist) (1925-2018), Indian printmaker and sculptor *Krishna S. Reddy (1916–), Fiji Indian school teacher and member of the Legislative Council * S. V. Krishna Reddy (born 1966), Indian film director * Vishal Krishna Reddy (born 1977), Indian film actor
title: Krishna Reddy
